7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-gray-900 pb-10 mb-10\"><h2 class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-600 mb-4\">Response Times</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-[#111] border border-gray-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock text-blue-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div><p class=\"text-white font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\">WhatsApp</p><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs\">Typically within <strong class=\"text-white\">a few hours</strong> during business hours. We aim to respond to all messages within 24 hours.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-white font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\">Email</p><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs\">Within <strong class=\"text-white\">1–2 business days</strong>. For urgent matters, WhatsApp is recommended.</p></div><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-xs border-t border-gray-900 pt-3 mt-3\">Business hours: Monday – Friday, 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM (Malaysia Time, UTC+8). We may respond outside these hours but cannot guarantee it.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-gray-900 pb-10 mb-10\"><h2 class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-600 mb-4\">What to Include in Your Message</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><p>To help us resolve your enquiry as quickly as possible, please include the following where applicable:</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-500\"><li><strong class=\"text-white\">Order reference number</strong> — found in your order confirmation or WhatsApp notification</li><li><strong class=\"text-white\">Your name</strong> as provided during checkout</li><li><strong class=\"text-white\">Description of the issue</strong> — with photos if your enquiry relates to condition, damage, or returns</li><li><strong class=\"text-white\">Your preferred resolution</strong> — refund, replacement, or other</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-gray-900 pb-10 mb-10\"><h2 class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-600 mb-4\">Types of Enquiries</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg\"><p class=\"text-white font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-3\">Order &amp; Payment</p><ul class=\"space-y-1\"><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Payment confirmation</li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Order status</li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Pre-order timelines</li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Invoice requests</li></ul></div><div class=\"border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg\"><p class=\"text-white font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-3\">Shipping &amp; Delivery</p><ul class=\"space-y-1\"><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Tracking numbers</li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Delayed deliveries</li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Failed delivery</li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Address corrections</li></ul></div><div class=\"border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg\"><p class=\"text-white font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-3\">Returns &amp; Refunds</p><ul class=\"space-y-1\"><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Damaged items</li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Wrong item received</li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Refund status</li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Return logistics</li></ul></div><div class=\"border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg\"><p class=\"text-white font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest mb-3\">Product Enquiries</p><ul class=\"space-y-1\"><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Additional photos</li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Condition clarification</li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Authenticity verification</li><li class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full shrink-0\"></span>Product availability</li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-gray-900 pb-10 mb-10\"><h2 class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-blue-600 mb-4\">Data Protection Enquiries</h2><div class=\"space-y-4 text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed\"><p>For requests under the <strong class=\"text-white\">Personal Data Protection Act 2010 (PDPA)</strong> — including data access, correction, or withdrawal of consent — please contact us via email with the subject line <strong class=\"text-white\">“PDPA Data Request”</strong>. We will respond within <strong class=\"text-white\">21 business days</strong> and may require identity verification before processing the request.</p><p>See our <a class=\"text-blue-500 hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/privacy-policy/\">Privacy Policy</a> for full details on your data rights.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-900 flex flex-wrap gap-6\"><a class=\"text-blue-600 hover:text-white font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] transition-colors\" href=\"/about/\">About Us</a><a class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-400 font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] transition-colors\" href=\"/terms/\">Terms &amp; Conditions</a><a class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-400 font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] transition-colors\" href=\"/privacy-policy/\">Privacy Policy</a><a class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-400 font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] transition-colors\" href=\"/return-policy/\">Return &amp; Refund Policy</a></div></div></main></div><script>$RB=[];$RV=function(a){$RT=performance.now();for(var b=0;b<a.length;b+=2){var c=a[b],e=a[b+1];null!==e.parentNode&&e.parentNode.removeChild(e);var f=c.parentNode;if(f){var g=c.previousSibling,h=0;do{if(c&&8===c.nodeType){var d=c.data;if(\"/$\"===d||\"/&\"===d)if(0===h)break;else h--;else\"$\"!==d&&\"$?\"!==d&&\"$~\"!==d&&\"$!\"!==d&&\"&\"!==d||h++}d=c.nextSibling;f.removeChild(c);c=d}while(c);for(;e.firstChild;)f.insertBefore(e.firstChild,c);g.data=\"$\";g._reactRetry&&requestAnimationFrame(g._reactRetry)}}a.length=0};\n$RC=function(a,b){if(b=document.getElementById(b))(a=document.getElementById(